OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start, with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of light rain and drizzle at
OL,7,Ftimes, especially over Derbyshire
OL,8,Fhills. Becoming mostly dry into the
OL,9,Fafternoon with some bright or sunny
OL,10,Fspells developing. Chance of the odd
OL,11,Fshower. Feeling noticeably milder.
OL,12,FLight winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FAny showers fading to leave a
OL,15,Fdry night, with variable amounts of
OL,16,Fcloud and clear spells. Perhaps a few
OL,17,Fmist or fog patches forming by dawn.
OL,18,FLocally chilly. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
