OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FEarly mist and fog patches
OL,6,Fsoon clearing to give a mostly fine
OL,7,Fand dry day, with variable amounts of
OL,8,Fcloud and bright or sunny spells.
OL,9,FLight winds. Rain arriving overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FEarly
OL,12,Frain clearing to give mostly fine and
OL,13,Fdry conditions Thursday. Feeling
OL,14,Fcooler. Becoming unsettled with some
OL,15,Frain at times Friday and Saturday.
OL,16,FOften windy and relatively mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
